7.3 状态机设计
这是你方案里的灵魂。
状态
IDLE
TRACKING
RID_MATCHED
SUSPICIOUS
HIGH_RISK
EVENT_LOCKED
COOP_GUARD
CRASH_ALERT
转移
有目标进入：IDLE → TRACKING
匹配到合法身份：TRACKING → RID_MATCHED
长时间未匹配：TRACKING → SUSPICIOUS
风险评分高：SUSPICIOUS → HIGH_RISK
抓拍完成并上云：HIGH_RISK → EVENT_LOCKED
合法目标启用守护：RID_MATCHED → COOP_GUARD
异常声学 + 高速下降：COOP_GUARD → CRASH_ALERT
